  "description": "The practice of mining Bitcoin from a residence or small office using low-to-medium power hardware. Contrasts with industrial-scale mining in dedicated facilities. Home mining has seen a resurgence with the rise of efficient, quiet, open-source ASICs and hashrate marketplaces that let participants rent industrial-scale hash without owning hardware.",
